-- =============================================================================
-- Neon Visuals — Seed Collections I/J/K (004): bucket rows, image_url column,
-- and 29 new product SKUs.
-- Split from the enum extension (003) because a new enum value cannot be used in
-- the same transaction that adds it — 003 commits first, so 'I'/'J'/'K' are safe
-- to reference here.
-- Additive only (ALTER/INSERT). No DROP, no CREATE TABLE, RLS untouched.
-- Prices intentionally left NULL (the public site reads from static no-price data
-- files; these columns are internal-only and not yet priced for these SKUs).
-- =============================================================================

